{
  "stem": "7556.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe they would find me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And certainly if they would, they would kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were going from house to house, from apartment to apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people tried to hide, and some were more lucky than others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we felt, as I mentioned before, that because we were young and we are able to work, that maybe it's a better thing to go and stay on the street rather than to hide under the bed or someplace where they can very easily find you.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean who did they take?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, and they were going to concentration camps, or camps where they just put them to sleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they already decided that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German on the spot, if you were too old or not straight or didn't seem to be strong enough to work, you were the first one to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Children were-- some parents tried to save themselves, so they-- I don't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably when they close the ghetto and they finished the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they told us all to get out, and they marched us to the Plaszow, the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you look back and the streets were empty, and some people that were either sick or too old who were standing at the windows and looking at the rest of us marching away, and--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whoever was able to walk, sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were soldiers, the Germans, with guns and watching you, marching alongside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think very few, very little, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
